Second version of the map as the first had an illegal porting of the Red and Blu logos from TF2, ended up making my own. Random Exquisite Destruction for T team and Brutal Law Unit for CT.

This map has 48 spawn points, HDR and buyzones.

Thanks go to:

Ryan for the custom dev textures
Karatekaefer for the custom skybox

Please assess if you like it.
